Messages.Value: Thank you for calling the travel agency, my name is Noah Wilson. How can I assist you today?

Hi Noah, my name is Jane Smith and I'm calling because I have a complaint regarding my recent trip. I went from Los Angeles to New York City last week, and my luggage never arrived at my hotel. I've been trying to track it down with the airline but haven't had any luck so far.
I'm so sorry to hear that, Jane. Losing luggage can be a very frustrating experience. Can you please provide me with your booking details so I can look into this for you?
Yes, my reservation number is ABC123 and I flew with American Airlines on May 1st at 11AM from LAX to JFK.

Thank you for providing that information, Jane. Let me check with both the airline and the hotel to see if they have any information about your luggage. I will follow up with you once I have an update.
Thank you, Noah. I appreciate your help.
